        SELECT  ?coded_var
                ?tech_name
                ?kaikki
                ?heading
                ?unit
                ?jno
                ?rules
                ?presision
                ?decimals
                ?method
                ?filabel
                ?enlabel
                ?svlabel
                ?fidesc
                ?svdesc
                ?endesc

        FROM tilasto:tilastot_ktutk

        WHERE {
            ?pxfile pxt:tableId "14qa" .
            ?pxfile ?kaikki ?dimemsions.
            ?dimemsions pxt:isHeading ?heading .



            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name rdfs:label ?filabel_s .
                BIND (STR(?filabel_s)  AS ?filabel)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?filabel_s),"fi") )
            }
            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name rdfs:label ?enlabel_s .
                BIND (STR(?enlabel_s)  AS ?enlabel)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?enlabel_s),"en") )
            }
            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name rdfs:label ?svlabel_s .
                BIND (STR(?svlabel_s)  AS ?svlabel)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?svlabel_s),"sv") )
            }
            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name dc:description ?fidesc_s .
                BIND (STR(?fidesc_s)  AS ?fidesc)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?fidesc_s),"fi") )
            }
            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name dc:description ?svdesc_s .
                BIND (STR(?svdesc_s)  AS ?svdesc)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?svdesc_s),"sv") )
            }
            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name dc:description ?endesc_s .
                BIND (STR(?endesc_s)  AS ?endesc)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?endesc_s),"en") )
            }

            ?dimemsions pxt:hasNumericalVariable ?coded_var .

            ?coded_var pxt:hasSequenceNumber ?jno .
            ?coded_var pxt:hasPrecision ?presision.
            OPTIONAL {
            ?coded_var pxt:decimals ?decimals.
            }
            ?coded_var pxt:isPresentationOfDescribedValueDomain ?d .
            ?tech_name gsimsf:hasDescribedValueDomain ?d .
            ?d gsimsf:hasProcessingRules ?rules.
            ?d gsimsf:hasAggregationMethod ?method.
            ?d gsimsf:hasUnit ?unit.


        }
run update, query_formatted:  stat:               <http://www.stat.fi/>

{ GRAPH tilasto:tilastot_ktutk

	}

INSERT
{ GRAPH tilasto:tilastot_ktutk
	{
	   
		?cube   cubemeta:source " kotitalouksien kulutus"@fi ;
				cubemeta:source " hush√•llens konsumtion"@sv ;
				cubemeta:source "households' consumption "@en .
	}
}
WHERE
{ GRAPH tilasto:tilastot_ktutk
	{
		?pxfile pxt:tableId "14qa" .
		?pxfile pxt:isPresentationOf ?cube .

		?cube cubemeta:source ?text .
		
	}
}
run query, query_formatted:  stat:               <http://www.stat.fi/>

            

                SELECT ?updated_date ?user
                FROM tilasto:tilastot_ktutk
                WHERE {
                    ?pxfile pxt:tableId "14qa".
                    ?pxfile pxt:isPresentationOf ?cube.
                    ?cube cubemeta:lastUpdated ?updated_date.
                  ?cube cubemeta:modifier ?user.
                }
run update, query_formatted:  stat:               <http://www.stat.fi/>

            

                DELETE
                { GRAPH tilasto:tilastot_ktutk
                    {
                        ?pxfile pxt:tableId "14qa" .
                        ?pxfile pxt:isPresentationOf ?cube .
                        ?cube cubemeta:lastUpdated ?updated_date .
                        ?cube cubemeta:modifier ?user .
                    }
                }
                INSERT
                { GRAPH tilasto:tilastot_ktutk
                    {
                        ?pxfile pxt:tableId "14qa".
                        ?pxfile pxt:isPresentationOf ?cube.
                        ?cube cubemeta:lastUpdated ?timeVal .
                        ?cube cubemeta:modifier "Miettinj" .
                    }
                }
                WHERE
                { GRAPH tilasto:tilastot_ktutk
                    {
                        ?pxfile pxt:tableId "14qa".
                        ?pxfile pxt:isPresentationOf ?cube.
                        ?cube cubemeta:lastUpdated ?updated_date.
                        ?cube cubemeta:modifier ?user.
    					BIND(now() AS ?timeVal) .
                    }
				}
run query, query_formatted:  stat:               <http://www.stat.fi/>

            
         
SELECT   
?filabel
?enlabel 
?svlabel
?fidesc
?svdesc
?endesc
?finote
?ennote
?svnote
?fisource
?ensource
?svsource
?ficontact
?encontact
?svcontact

                FROM tilasto:tilastot_ktutk

                WHERE {


                    OPTIONAL {
                        cubemeta:CubeMeta\/14qa dc:title ?filabel_s .
                        BIND (STR(?filabel_s)  AS ?filabel)
                        FILTER( langMatches(lang(?filabel_s),"fi") )
                    }
                    OPTIONAL {
                        cubemeta:CubeMeta\/14qa dc:title ?svlabel_s .
                        BIND (STR(?svlabel_s)  AS ?svlabel)
                        FILTER( langMatches(lang(?svlabel_s),"sv") )
                    }
                    OPTIONAL {
                        cubemeta:CubeMeta\/14qa dc:title ?enlabel_s .
                        BIND (STR(?enlabel_s)  AS ?enlabel)
                        FILTER( langMatches(lang(?enlabel_s),"en") )
                    }
                    OPTIONAL {
                        cubemeta:CubeMeta\/14qa dc:description ?fidesc_s .
                        BIND (STR(?fidesc_s)  AS ?fidesc)
                        FILTER( langMatches(lang(?fidesc_s),"fi") )
                    }
                    OPTIONAL {
                        cubemeta:CubeMeta\/14qa dc:description ?svdesc_s .
                        BIND (STR(?svdesc_s)  AS ?svdesc)
                        FILTER( langMatches(lang(?svdesc_s),"sv") )
                    }
                    OPTIONAL {
                        cubemeta:CubeMeta\/14qa dc:description ?endesc_s .
                        BIND (STR(?endesc_s)  AS ?endesc)
                        FILTER( langMatches(lang(?endesc_s),"en") )
                    }
                    OPTIONAL {
                        cubemeta:CubeMeta\/14qa cubemeta:tableNote ?finote_s .
                        BIND (STR(?finote_s)  AS ?finote)
                        FILTER( langMatches(lang(?finote_s),"fi") )
                    }
                    OPTIONAL {
                        cubemeta:CubeMeta\/14qa cubemeta:tableNote ?svnote_s .
                        BIND (STR(?svnote_s)  AS ?svnote)
                        FILTER( langMatches(lang(?svnote_s),"sv") )
                    }
                    OPTIONAL {
                        cubemeta:CubeMeta\/14qa cubemeta:tableNote ?ennote_s .
                        BIND (STR(?ennote_s)  AS ?ennote)
                        FILTER( langMatches(lang(?ennote_s),"en") )
                    }
                    OPTIONAL {
                        cubemeta:CubeMeta\/14qa cubemeta:source ?fisource_s .
                        BIND (STR(?fisource_s)  AS ?fisource)
                        FILTER( langMatches(lang(?fisource_s),"fi") )
                    }
                    OPTIONAL {
                        cubemeta:CubeMeta\/14qa cubemeta:source ?svsource_s .
                        BIND (STR(?svsource_s)  AS ?svsource)
                        FILTER( langMatches(lang(?svsource_s),"sv") )
                    }
                    OPTIONAL {
                        cubemeta:CubeMeta\/14qa cubemeta:source ?ensource_s .
                        BIND (STR(?ensource_s)  AS ?ensource)
                        FILTER( langMatches(lang(?ensource_s),"en") )
                    }
                    OPTIONAL {
                        cubemeta:CubeMeta\/14qa cubemeta:contact ?ficontact_s .
                        BIND (STR(?ficontact_s)  AS ?ficontact)
                        FILTER( langMatches(lang(?ficontact_s),"fi") )
                    }
                    OPTIONAL {
                        cubemeta:CubeMeta\/14qa cubemeta:contact ?svcontact_s .
                        BIND (STR(?svcontact_s)  AS ?svcontact)
                        FILTER( langMatches(lang(?svcontact_s),"sv") )
                    }
                    OPTIONAL {
                        cubemeta:CubeMeta\/14qa cubemeta:contact ?encontact_s .
                        BIND (STR(?encontact_s)  AS ?encontact)
                        FILTER( langMatches(lang(?encontact_s),"en") )
                    }

                }
run query, query_formatted:  stat:               <http://www.stat.fi/>

        SELECT  ?coded_var
                ?tech_name
                ?kaikki
                ?heading
                ?unit
                ?jno
                ?rules
                ?presision
                ?decimals
                ?method
                ?filabel
                ?enlabel
                ?svlabel
                ?fidesc
                ?svdesc
                ?endesc

        FROM tilasto:tilastot_ktutk

        WHERE {
            ?pxfile pxt:tableId "14qa" .
            ?pxfile ?kaikki ?dimemsions.
            ?dimemsions pxt:isHeading ?heading .



            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name rdfs:label ?filabel_s .
                BIND (STR(?filabel_s)  AS ?filabel)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?filabel_s),"fi") )
            }
            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name rdfs:label ?enlabel_s .
                BIND (STR(?enlabel_s)  AS ?enlabel)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?enlabel_s),"en") )
            }
            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name rdfs:label ?svlabel_s .
                BIND (STR(?svlabel_s)  AS ?svlabel)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?svlabel_s),"sv") )
            }
            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name dc:description ?fidesc_s .
                BIND (STR(?fidesc_s)  AS ?fidesc)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?fidesc_s),"fi") )
            }
            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name dc:description ?svdesc_s .
                BIND (STR(?svdesc_s)  AS ?svdesc)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?svdesc_s),"sv") )
            }
            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name dc:description ?endesc_s .
                BIND (STR(?endesc_s)  AS ?endesc)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?endesc_s),"en") )
            }

            ?dimemsions pxt:hasNumericalVariable ?coded_var .

            ?coded_var pxt:hasSequenceNumber ?jno .
            ?coded_var pxt:hasPrecision ?presision.
            OPTIONAL {
            ?coded_var pxt:decimals ?decimals.
            }
            ?coded_var pxt:isPresentationOfDescribedValueDomain ?d .
            ?tech_name gsimsf:hasDescribedValueDomain ?d .
            ?d gsimsf:hasProcessingRules ?rules.
            ?d gsimsf:hasAggregationMethod ?method.
            ?d gsimsf:hasUnit ?unit.


        }
run query, query_formatted:  stat:               <http://www.stat.fi/>

            

        SELECT  ?coded_var
                ?tech_name
                ?kaikki
                ?heading
                ?unit
                ?jno
                ?rules
                ?presision
                ?decimals
                ?method
                ?filabel
                ?enlabel
                ?svlabel
                ?fidesc
                ?svdesc
                ?endesc

        FROM tilasto:tilastot_ktutk

        WHERE {
            ?pxfile pxt:tableId "14ph" .
            ?pxfile ?kaikki ?dimemsions.
            ?dimemsions pxt:isHeading ?heading .



            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name rdfs:label ?filabel_s .

                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?filabel_s),"fi") )

                BIND (STR(?endesc_s)  AS ?endesc)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?endesc_s),"en") )
            }

            ?dimemsions pxt:hasNumericalVariable ?coded_var .

            ?coded_var pxt:hasSequenceNumber ?jno .
            ?coded_var pxt:hasPrecision ?presision.
            OPTIONAL {
            ?coded_var pxt:decimals ?decimals.
            }
            ?coded_var pxt:isPresentationOfDescribedValueDomain ?d .
            ?tech_name gsimsf:hasDescribedValueDomain ?d .
            ?d gsimsf:hasProcessingRules ?rules.
            ?d gsimsf:hasAggregationMethod ?method.
            ?d gsimsf:hasUnit ?unit.


        }

        SELECT  ?coded_var
                ?tech_name
                ?kaikki
                ?heading
                ?unit
                ?jno
                ?rules
                ?presision
                ?decimals
                ?method
                ?filabel
                ?enlabel
                ?svlabel
                ?fidesc
                ?svdesc
                ?endesc

        FROM tilasto:tilastot_ktutk

        WHERE {
            ?pxfile pxt:tableId "14ph" .
            ?pxfile ?kaikki ?dimemsions.
            ?dimemsions pxt:isHeading ?heading .



            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name rdfs:label ?filabel_s .
                BIND (STR(?filabel_s)  AS ?filabel)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?filabel_s),"fi") )
            }
            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name rdfs:label ?enlabel_s .
                BIND (STR(?enlabel_s)  AS ?enlabel)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?enlabel_s),"en") )
            }
            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name rdfs:label ?svlabel_s .
                BIND (STR(?svlabel_s)  AS ?svlabel)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?svlabel_s),"sv") )
            }
            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name dc:description ?fidesc_s .
                BIND (STR(?fidesc_s)  AS ?fidesc)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?fidesc_s),"fi") )
            }
            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name dc:description ?svdesc_s .
                BIND (STR(?svdesc_s)  AS ?svdesc)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?svdesc_s),"sv") )
            }
            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name dc:description ?endesc_s .
                BIND (STR(?endesc_s)  AS ?endesc)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?endesc_s),"en") )
            }

            ?dimemsions pxt:hasNumericalVariable ?coded_var .

            ?coded_var pxt:hasSequenceNumber ?jno .
            ?coded_var pxt:hasPrecision ?presision.
            OPTIONAL {
            ?coded_var pxt:decimals ?decimals.
            }
            ?coded_var pxt:isPresentationOfDescribedValueDomain ?d .
            ?tech_name gsimsf:hasDescribedValueDomain ?d .
            ?d gsimsf:hasProcessingRules ?rules.
            ?d gsimsf:hasAggregationMethod ?method.
            ?d gsimsf:hasUnit ?unit.


        }

        SELECT  ?coded_var
                ?tech_name
                ?kaikki
                ?heading
                ?unit
                ?jno
                ?rules
                ?presision
                ?decimals
                ?method
                ?filabel
                ?enlabel
                ?svlabel
                ?fidesc
                ?svdesc
                ?endesc

        FROM tilasto:tilastot_ktutk

        WHERE {
            ?pxfile pxt:tableId "14ph" .
            ?pxfile ?kaikki ?dimemsions.
            ?dimemsions pxt:isHeading ?heading .



            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name rdfs:label ?filabel_s .
                BIND (STR(?filabel_s)  AS ?filabel)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?filabel_s),"fi") )
            }
            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name rdfs:label ?enlabel_s .
                BIND (STR(?enlabel_s)  AS ?enlabel)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?enlabel_s),"en") )
            }
            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name rdfs:label ?svlabel_s .
                BIND (STR(?svlabel_s)  AS ?svlabel)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?svlabel_s),"sv") )
            }
            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name dc:description ?fidesc_s .
                BIND (STR(?fidesc_s)  AS ?fidesc)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?fidesc_s),"fi") )
            }
            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name dc:description ?svdesc_s .
                BIND (STR(?svdesc_s)  AS ?svdesc)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?svdesc_s),"sv") )
            }
            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name dc:description ?endesc_s .
                BIND (STR(?endesc_s)  AS ?endesc)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?endesc_s),"en") )
            }

            ?dimemsions pxt:hasNumericalVariable ?coded_var .

            ?coded_var pxt:hasSequenceNumber ?jno .
            ?coded_var pxt:hasPrecision ?presision.
            OPTIONAL {
            ?coded_var pxt:decimals ?decimals.
            }
            ?coded_var pxt:isPresentationOfDescribedValueDomain ?d .
            ?tech_name gsimsf:hasDescribedValueDomain ?d .
            ?d gsimsf:hasProcessingRules ?rules.
            ?d gsimsf:hasAggregationMethod ?method.
            ?d gsimsf:hasUnit ?unit.


        }
run update, query_formatted:  stat:               <http://www.stat.fi/>

                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?svdesc_s),"sv") )
            }
            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name dc:description ?endesc_s .
                BIND (STR(?endesc_s)  AS ?endesc)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?endesc_s),"en") )
            }

            ?dimemsions pxt:hasNumericalVariable ?coded_var .

            ?coded_var pxt:hasSequenceNumber ?jno .
            ?coded_var pxt:hasPrecision ?presision.
            OPTIONAL {
            ?coded_var pxt:decimals ?decimals.
            }
            ?coded_var pxt:isPresentationOfDescribedValueDomain ?d .
            ?tech_name gsimsf:hasDescribedValueDomain ?d .
            ?d gsimsf:hasProcessingRules ?rules.
            ?d gsimsf:hasAggregationMethod ?method.
            ?d gsimsf:hasUnit ?unit.

        SELECT  ?coded_var
                ?tech_name
                ?kaikki
                ?heading
                ?unit
                ?jno
                ?rules
                ?presision
                ?decimals
                ?method
                ?filabel
                ?enlabel
                ?svlabel
                ?fidesc
                ?svdesc
                ?endesc

        FROM tilasto:tilastot_ktutk

        WHERE {
            ?pxfile pxt:tableId "14ph" .
            ?pxfile ?kaikki ?dimemsions.
            ?dimemsions pxt:isHeading ?heading .



            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name rdfs:label ?filabel_s .
                BIND (STR(?filabel_s)  AS ?filabel)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?filabel_s),"fi") )
            }
            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name rdfs:label ?enlabel_s .

            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name rdfs:label ?svlabel_s .
                BIND (STR(?svlabel_s)  AS ?svlabel)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?svlabel_s),"sv") )
            }
            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name dc:description ?fidesc_s .
                BIND (STR(?fidesc_s)  AS ?fidesc)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?fidesc_s),"fi") )
            }
            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name dc:description ?svdesc_s .
                BIND (STR(?svdesc_s)  AS ?svdesc)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?svdesc_s),"sv") )
            }
            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name dc:description ?endesc_s .
                BIND (STR(?endesc_s)  AS ?endesc)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?endesc_s),"en") )
            }

            ?dimemsions pxt:hasNumericalVariable ?coded_var .

            ?coded_var pxt:hasSequenceNumber ?jno .
            ?coded_var pxt:hasPrecision ?presision.
            OPTIONAL {
            ?coded_var pxt:decimals ?decimals.

run update, query_formatted:  stat:               <http://www.stat.fi/>

            
                    
DELETE
{ GRAPH tilasto:tilastot_ktutk
	{
		?cube cubemeta:source ?text .
	   
	}
}
INSERT
{ GRAPH tilasto:tilastot_ktutk
	{
	   
		?cube   cubemeta:source " kotitalouksien kulutus"@fi ;
				cubemeta:source " hush√•llens konsumtion"@sv ;
				cubemeta:source "households' consumption "@en .
	}
}
WHERE
{ GRAPH tilasto:tilastot_ktutk
	{
		?pxfile pxt:tableId "14ph" .
		?pxfile pxt:isPresentationOf ?cube .

		?cube cubemeta:source ?text .
		
	}
}
run query, query_formatted:  stat:               <http://www.stat.fi/>

            

                SELECT ?updated_date ?user
                FROM tilasto:tilastot_ktutk
                WHERE {
                    ?pxfile pxt:tableId "14ph".
                    ?pxfile pxt:isPresentationOf ?cube.
                    ?cube cubemeta:lastUpdated ?updated_date.
                  ?cube cubemeta:modifier ?user.
                }
run update, query_formatted:  stat:               <http://www.stat.fi/>

            

                DELETE
                { GRAPH tilasto:tilastot_ktutk
                    {
                        ?pxfile pxt:tableId "14ph" .
                        ?pxfile pxt:isPresentationOf ?cube .
                        ?cube cubemeta:lastUpdated ?updated_date .
                        ?cube cubemeta:modifier ?user .
                    }
                }
                INSERT
                { GRAPH tilasto:tilastot_ktutk
                    {
                        ?pxfile pxt:tableId "14ph".
                        ?pxfile pxt:isPresentationOf ?cube.
                        ?cube cubemeta:lastUpdated ?timeVal .
                        ?cube cubemeta:modifier "Miettinj" .
                    }
                }
                WHERE
                { GRAPH tilasto:tilastot_ktutk
                    {
                        ?pxfile pxt:tableId "14ph".
                        ?pxfile pxt:isPresentationOf ?cube.
                        ?cube cubemeta:lastUpdated ?updated_date.
                        ?cube cubemeta:modifier ?user.
    					BIND(now() AS ?timeVal) .
                    }
				}
run query, query_formatted:  stat:               <http://www.stat.fi/>

            
         
SELECT   
?filabel
?enlabel 
?svlabel
?fidesc
?svdesc
?endesc
?finote
?ennote
?svnote
?fisource
?ensource
?svsource
?ficontact
?encontact
?svcontact

                FROM tilasto:tilastot_ktutk

                WHERE {


                    OPTIONAL {
                        cubemeta:CubeMeta\/14ph dc:title ?filabel_s .
                        BIND (STR(?filabel_s)  AS ?filabel)
                        FILTER( langMatches(lang(?filabel_s),"fi") )
                    }
                    OPTIONAL {
                        cubemeta:CubeMeta\/14ph dc:title ?svlabel_s .
                        BIND (STR(?svlabel_s)  AS ?svlabel)
                        FILTER( langMatches(lang(?svlabel_s),"sv") )
                    }
                    OPTIONAL {
                        cubemeta:CubeMeta\/14ph dc:title ?enlabel_s .
                        BIND (STR(?enlabel_s)  AS ?enlabel)
                        FILTER( langMatches(lang(?enlabel_s),"en") )
                    }
                    OPTIONAL {
                        cubemeta:CubeMeta\/14ph dc:description ?fidesc_s .
                        BIND (STR(?fidesc_s)  AS ?fidesc)
                        FILTER( langMatches(lang(?fidesc_s),"fi") )
                    }
                    OPTIONAL {
                        cubemeta:CubeMeta\/14ph dc:description ?svdesc_s .
                        BIND (STR(?svdesc_s)  AS ?svdesc)
                        FILTER( langMatches(lang(?svdesc_s),"sv") )
                    }
                    OPTIONAL {
                        cubemeta:CubeMeta\/14ph dc:description ?endesc_s .
                        BIND (STR(?endesc_s)  AS ?endesc)
                        FILTER( langMatches(lang(?endesc_s),"en") )
                    }
                    OPTIONAL {
                        cubemeta:CubeMeta\/14ph cubemeta:tableNote ?finote_s .
                        BIND (STR(?finote_s)  AS ?finote)
                        FILTER( langMatches(lang(?finote_s),"fi") )
                    }
                    OPTIONAL {
                        cubemeta:CubeMeta\/14ph cubemeta:tableNote ?svnote_s .
                        BIND (STR(?svnote_s)  AS ?svnote)
                        FILTER( langMatches(lang(?svnote_s),"sv") )
                    }
                    OPTIONAL {
                        cubemeta:CubeMeta\/14ph cubemeta:tableNote ?ennote_s .
                        BIND (STR(?ennote_s)  AS ?ennote)
                        FILTER( langMatches(lang(?ennote_s),"en") )
                    }
                    OPTIONAL {
                        cubemeta:CubeMeta\/14ph cubemeta:source ?fisource_s .
                        BIND (STR(?fisource_s)  AS ?fisource)
                        FILTER( langMatches(lang(?fisource_s),"fi") )
                    }
                    OPTIONAL {
                        cubemeta:CubeMeta\/14ph cubemeta:source ?svsource_s .
                        BIND (STR(?svsource_s)  AS ?svsource)
                        FILTER( langMatches(lang(?svsource_s),"sv") )
                    }
                    OPTIONAL {
                        cubemeta:CubeMeta\/14ph cubemeta:source ?ensource_s .
                        BIND (STR(?ensource_s)  AS ?ensource)
                        FILTER( langMatches(lang(?ensource_s),"en") )
                    }
                    OPTIONAL {
                        cubemeta:CubeMeta\/14ph cubemeta:contact ?ficontact_s .
                        BIND (STR(?ficontact_s)  AS ?ficontact)
                        FILTER( langMatches(lang(?ficontact_s),"fi") )
                    }
                    OPTIONAL {
                        cubemeta:CubeMeta\/14ph cubemeta:contact ?svcontact_s .
                        BIND (STR(?svcontact_s)  AS ?svcontact)
                        FILTER( langMatches(lang(?svcontact_s),"sv") )
                    }
                    OPTIONAL {
                        cubemeta:CubeMeta\/14ph cubemeta:contact ?encontact_s .
                        BIND (STR(?encontact_s)  AS ?encontact)
                        FILTER( langMatches(lang(?encontact_s),"en") )
                    }

                }
run query, query_formatted:  stat:               <http://www.stat.fi/>

        SELECT  ?coded_var
                ?tech_name
                ?kaikki
                ?heading
                ?unit
                ?jno
                ?rules
                ?presision
                ?decimals
                ?method
                ?filabel
                ?enlabel
                ?svlabel
                ?fidesc
                ?svdesc
                ?endesc

        FROM tilasto:tilastot_ktutk

        WHERE {
            ?pxfile pxt:tableId "14ph" .
            ?pxfile ?kaikki ?dimemsions.
            ?dimemsions pxt:isHeading ?heading .



            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name rdfs:label ?filabel_s .
                BIND (STR(?filabel_s)  AS ?filabel)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?filabel_s),"fi") )
            }
            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name rdfs:label ?enlabel_s .
                BIND (STR(?enlabel_s)  AS ?enlabel)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?enlabel_s),"en") )
            }
            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name rdfs:label ?svlabel_s .
                BIND (STR(?svlabel_s)  AS ?svlabel)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?svlabel_s),"sv") )
            }
            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name dc:description ?fidesc_s .
                BIND (STR(?fidesc_s)  AS ?fidesc)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?fidesc_s),"fi") )
            }
            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name dc:description ?svdesc_s .
                BIND (STR(?svdesc_s)  AS ?svdesc)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?svdesc_s),"sv") )
            }
            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name dc:description ?endesc_s .
                BIND (STR(?endesc_s)  AS ?endesc)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?endesc_s),"en") )
            }

            ?dimemsions pxt:hasNumericalVariable ?coded_var .

            ?coded_var pxt:hasSequenceNumber ?jno .
            ?coded_var pxt:hasPrecision ?presision.
            OPTIONAL {
            ?coded_var pxt:decimals ?decimals.
            }
            ?coded_var pxt:isPresentationOfDescribedValueDomain ?d .
            ?tech_name gsimsf:hasDescribedValueDomain ?d .
            ?d gsimsf:hasProcessingRules ?rules.
            ?d gsimsf:hasAggregationMethod ?method.
            ?d gsimsf:hasUnit ?unit.


        }
run query, query_formatted:  stat:               <http://www.stat.fi/>

            

        SELECT  ?coded_var
                ?tech_name
                ?kaikki
                ?heading
                ?unit

                ?enlabel

        SELECT  ?coded_var
                ?tech_name
                ?kaikki
                ?heading
                ?unit
                ?jno
                ?rules
                ?presision
                ?decimals
                ?method
                ?filabel
                ?enlabel
                ?svlabel
                ?fidesc
                ?svdesc
                ?endesc

        FROM tilasto:tilastot_ktutk

        WHERE {
            ?pxfile pxt:tableId "14lv" .
            ?pxfile ?kaikki ?dimemsions.
            ?dimemsions pxt:isHeading ?heading .



            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name rdfs:label ?filabel_s .
                BIND (STR(?filabel_s)  AS ?filabel)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?filabel_s),"fi") )
            }
            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name rdfs:label ?enlabel_s .
                BIND (STR(?enlabel_s)  AS ?enlabel)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?enlabel_s),"en") )
            }
            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name rdfs:label ?svlabel_s .
                BIND (STR(?svlabel_s)  AS ?svlabel)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?svlabel_s),"sv") )
            }
            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name dc:description ?fidesc_s .
                BIND (STR(?fidesc_s)  AS ?fidesc)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?fidesc_s),"fi") )
            }
            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name dc:description ?svdesc_s .
                BIND (STR(?svdesc_s)  AS ?svdesc)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?svdesc_s),"sv") )
            }
            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name dc:description ?endesc_s .
                BIND (STR(?endesc_s)  AS ?endesc)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?endesc_s),"en") )
            }

            ?dimemsions pxt:hasNumericalVariable ?coded_var .

            ?coded_var pxt:hasSequenceNumber ?jno .
            ?coded_var pxt:hasPrecision ?presision.
            OPTIONAL {
            ?coded_var pxt:decimals ?decimals.
            }
            ?coded_var pxt:isPresentationOfDescribedValueDomain ?d .
            ?tech_name gsimsf:hasDescribedValueDomain ?d .
            ?d gsimsf:hasProcessingRules ?rules.
            ?d gsimsf:hasAggregationMethod ?method.
            ?d gsimsf:hasUnit ?unit.


        }
run update, query_formatted:  stat:               <http://www.stat.fi/>

{ GRAPH tilasto:tilastot_ktutk
	{
		?cube cubemeta:source ?text .
	   
	}

INSERT
{ GRAPH tilasto:tilastot_ktutk
	{
	   
		?cube   cubemeta:source " kotitalouksien kulutus"@fi ;
				cubemeta:source " hush√•llens konsumtion"@sv ;
				cubemeta:source "households' consumption "@en .
	}
}
WHERE
{ GRAPH tilasto:tilastot_ktutk
	{
		?pxfile pxt:tableId "14lv" .
		?pxfile pxt:isPresentationOf ?cube .

		?cube cubemeta:source ?text .
		
	}
}
run query, query_formatted:  stat:               <http://www.stat.fi/>

            

                SELECT ?updated_date ?user
                FROM tilasto:tilastot_ktutk
                WHERE {
                    ?pxfile pxt:tableId "14lv".
                    ?pxfile pxt:isPresentationOf ?cube.
                    ?cube cubemeta:lastUpdated ?updated_date.
                  ?cube cubemeta:modifier ?user.
                }
run update, query_formatted:  stat:               <http://www.stat.fi/>

            

                DELETE
                { GRAPH tilasto:tilastot_ktutk
                    {
                        ?pxfile pxt:tableId "14lv" .
                        ?pxfile pxt:isPresentationOf ?cube .
                        ?cube cubemeta:lastUpdated ?updated_date .
                        ?cube cubemeta:modifier ?user .
                    }
                }
                INSERT
                { GRAPH tilasto:tilastot_ktutk
                    {
                        ?pxfile pxt:tableId "14lv".
                        ?pxfile pxt:isPresentationOf ?cube.
                        ?cube cubemeta:lastUpdated ?timeVal .
                        ?cube cubemeta:modifier "Miettinj" .
                    }
                }
                WHERE
                { GRAPH tilasto:tilastot_ktutk
                    {
                        ?pxfile pxt:tableId "14lv".
                        ?pxfile pxt:isPresentationOf ?cube.
                        ?cube cubemeta:lastUpdated ?updated_date.
                        ?cube cubemeta:modifier ?user.
    					BIND(now() AS ?timeVal) .
                    }
				}
run query, query_formatted:  stat:               <http://www.stat.fi/>

            
         
SELECT   
?filabel
?enlabel 
?svlabel
?fidesc
?svdesc
?endesc
?finote
?ennote
?svnote
?fisource
?ensource
?svsource
?ficontact
?encontact
?svcontact

                FROM tilasto:tilastot_ktutk

                WHERE {


                    OPTIONAL {
                        cubemeta:CubeMeta\/14lv dc:title ?filabel_s .
                        BIND (STR(?filabel_s)  AS ?filabel)
                        FILTER( langMatches(lang(?filabel_s),"fi") )
                    }
                    OPTIONAL {
                        cubemeta:CubeMeta\/14lv dc:title ?svlabel_s .
                        BIND (STR(?svlabel_s)  AS ?svlabel)
                        FILTER( langMatches(lang(?svlabel_s),"sv") )
                    }
                    OPTIONAL {
                        cubemeta:CubeMeta\/14lv dc:title ?enlabel_s .
                        BIND (STR(?enlabel_s)  AS ?enlabel)
                        FILTER( langMatches(lang(?enlabel_s),"en") )
                    }
                    OPTIONAL {
                        cubemeta:CubeMeta\/14lv dc:description ?fidesc_s .
                        BIND (STR(?fidesc_s)  AS ?fidesc)
                        FILTER( langMatches(lang(?fidesc_s),"fi") )
                    }
                    OPTIONAL {
                        cubemeta:CubeMeta\/14lv dc:description ?svdesc_s .
                        BIND (STR(?svdesc_s)  AS ?svdesc)
                        FILTER( langMatches(lang(?svdesc_s),"sv") )
                    }
                    OPTIONAL {
                        cubemeta:CubeMeta\/14lv dc:description ?endesc_s .
                        BIND (STR(?endesc_s)  AS ?endesc)
                        FILTER( langMatches(lang(?endesc_s),"en") )
                    }
                    OPTIONAL {
                        cubemeta:CubeMeta\/14lv cubemeta:tableNote ?finote_s .
                        BIND (STR(?finote_s)  AS ?finote)
                        FILTER( langMatches(lang(?finote_s),"fi") )
                    }
                    OPTIONAL {
                        cubemeta:CubeMeta\/14lv cubemeta:tableNote ?svnote_s .
                        BIND (STR(?svnote_s)  AS ?svnote)
                        FILTER( langMatches(lang(?svnote_s),"sv") )
                    }
                    OPTIONAL {
                        cubemeta:CubeMeta\/14lv cubemeta:tableNote ?ennote_s .
                        BIND (STR(?ennote_s)  AS ?ennote)
                        FILTER( langMatches(lang(?ennote_s),"en") )
                    }
                    OPTIONAL {
                        cubemeta:CubeMeta\/14lv cubemeta:source ?fisource_s .
                        BIND (STR(?fisource_s)  AS ?fisource)
                        FILTER( langMatches(lang(?fisource_s),"fi") )
                    }
                    OPTIONAL {
                        cubemeta:CubeMeta\/14lv cubemeta:source ?svsource_s .
                        BIND (STR(?svsource_s)  AS ?svsource)
                        FILTER( langMatches(lang(?svsource_s),"sv") )
                    }
                    OPTIONAL {
                        cubemeta:CubeMeta\/14lv cubemeta:source ?ensource_s .
                        BIND (STR(?ensource_s)  AS ?ensource)
                        FILTER( langMatches(lang(?ensource_s),"en") )
                    }
                    OPTIONAL {
                        cubemeta:CubeMeta\/14lv cubemeta:contact ?ficontact_s .
                        BIND (STR(?ficontact_s)  AS ?ficontact)
                        FILTER( langMatches(lang(?ficontact_s),"fi") )
                    }
                    OPTIONAL {
                        cubemeta:CubeMeta\/14lv cubemeta:contact ?svcontact_s .
                        BIND (STR(?svcontact_s)  AS ?svcontact)
                        FILTER( langMatches(lang(?svcontact_s),"sv") )
                    }
                    OPTIONAL {
                        cubemeta:CubeMeta\/14lv cubemeta:contact ?encontact_s .
                        BIND (STR(?encontact_s)  AS ?encontact)
                        FILTER( langMatches(lang(?encontact_s),"en") )
                    }

                }
run query, query_formatted:  stat:               <http://www.stat.fi/>

run query, query_formatted:  stat:               <http://www.stat.fi/>

            

        SELECT  ?coded_var
                ?tech_name
                ?kaikki
                ?heading
                ?unit
                ?jno
                ?rules
                ?presision
                ?decimals
                ?method
                ?filabel
                ?enlabel
                ?svlabel
                ?fidesc
                ?svdesc
                ?endesc

        FROM tilasto:tilastot_ktutk

        WHERE {
            ?pxfile pxt:tableId "14lv" .
            ?pxfile ?kaikki ?dimemsions.
            ?dimemsions pxt:isHeading ?heading .



            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name rdfs:label ?filabel_s .
                BIND (STR(?filabel_s)  AS ?filabel)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?filabel_s),"fi") )
            }
            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name rdfs:label ?enlabel_s .
                BIND (STR(?enlabel_s)  AS ?enlabel)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?enlabel_s),"en") )
            }
            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name rdfs:label ?svlabel_s .
                BIND (STR(?svlabel_s)  AS ?svlabel)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?svlabel_s),"sv") )
            }
            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name dc:description ?fidesc_s .
                BIND (STR(?fidesc_s)  AS ?fidesc)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?fidesc_s),"fi") )
            }
            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name dc:description ?svdesc_s .
                BIND (STR(?svdesc_s)  AS ?svdesc)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?svdesc_s),"sv") )
            }
            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name dc:description ?endesc_s .
                BIND (STR(?endesc_s)  AS ?endesc)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?endesc_s),"en") )
            }

            ?dimemsions pxt:hasNumericalVariable ?coded_var .

            ?coded_var pxt:hasSequenceNumber ?jno .
            ?coded_var pxt:hasPrecision ?presision.
            OPTIONAL {
            ?coded_var pxt:decimals ?decimals.
            }
            ?coded_var pxt:isPresentationOfDescribedValueDomain ?d .
            ?tech_name gsimsf:hasDescribedValueDomain ?d .
            ?d gsimsf:hasProcessingRules ?rules.
            ?d gsimsf:hasAggregationMethod ?method.
            ?d gsimsf:hasUnit ?unit.


        }
run query, query_formatted:  stat:               <http://www.stat.fi/>

            

        SELECT  ?coded_var
                ?tech_name
                ?kaikki
                ?heading
                ?unit
                ?jno
                ?rules
                ?presision
                ?decimals
                ?method
                ?filabel
                ?enlabel
                ?svlabel
                ?fidesc
                ?svdesc
                ?endesc

        FROM tilasto:tilastot_ktutk

        WHERE {
            ?pxfile pxt:tableId "12qn" .
            ?pxfile ?kaikki ?dimemsions.
            ?dimemsions pxt:isHeading ?heading .



            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name rdfs:label ?filabel_s .
                BIND (STR(?filabel_s)  AS ?filabel)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?filabel_s),"fi") )

                ?tech_name rdfs:label ?enlabel_s .
                BIND (STR(?enlabel_s)  AS ?enlabel)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?enlabel_s),"en") )

                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?fidesc_s),"fi") )
            }
            OPTIONAL {

                BIND (STR(?svdesc_s)  AS ?svdesc)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?svdesc_s),"sv") )
            }
            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name dc:description ?endesc_s .
                BIND (STR(?endesc_s)  AS ?endesc)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?endesc_s),"en") )
            }

            ?dimemsions pxt:hasNumericalVariable ?coded_var .

            ?coded_var pxt:hasSequenceNumber ?jno .
            ?coded_var pxt:hasPrecision ?presision.
            OPTIONAL {
            ?coded_var pxt:decimals ?decimals.
            }
            ?coded_var pxt:isPresentationOfDescribedValueDomain ?d .
            ?tech_name gsimsf:hasDescribedValueDomain ?d .
            ?d gsimsf:hasProcessingRules ?rules.
            ?d gsimsf:hasAggregationMethod ?method.
            ?d gsimsf:hasUnit ?unit.


        }
run update, query_formatted:  stat:               <http://www.stat.fi/>

            
			DELETE 
                { GRAPH tilasto:tilastot_ktutk
                    {

                    pxt:PxNumericalVariable\/12qn\/A01_osuus a pxt_ont:PxNumericalVariable ;
                                        pxt:hasSequenceNumber ?NRO ;
                                        pxt:hasPrecision ?PRES ;
                                        pxt:decimals ?DESIM ;
                                        pxt:isPresentationOfDescribedValueDomain gsimsf:DescribedValueDomain\/A01_osuus .
                    }
                }			
            INSERT 
                { GRAPH tilasto:tilastot_ktutk
                    {

                    pxt:PxNumericalVariable\/12qn\/A01_osuus a pxt_ont:PxNumericalVariable ;
                                        pxt:hasSequenceNumber 1 ;
                                        pxt:hasPrecision 0 ;
                                        pxt:decimals 0 ;
                                        pxt:isPresentationOfDescribedValueDomain gsimsf:DescribedValueDomain\/A01_osuus .
                    }
                }
			WHERE
                { GRAPH tilasto:tilastot_ktutk
                    {

                    pxt:PxNumericalVariable\/12qn\/A01_osuus a pxt_ont:PxNumericalVariable ;
                                        pxt:hasSequenceNumber ?NRO ;
                                        pxt:hasPrecision ?PRES ;
                                        pxt:decimals ?DESIM ;
                                        pxt:isPresentationOfDescribedValueDomain gsimsf:DescribedValueDomain\/A01_osuus .
                    }
                }				

run update, query_formatted:  stat:               <http://www.stat.fi/>

            

            DELETE
            { GRAPH tilasto:tilastot_ktutk
                {
                    pxt:PxNumericalVariable\/12qn\/A01_osuus pxt:hasPrecision ?precision ;
                                         pxt:decimals ?decimals ;
                                         pxt:isPresentationOfDescribedValueDomain ?desdom .
                    ?desdom gsimsf:hasUnit ?unit .

                }
            }
            INSERT
            { GRAPH tilasto:tilastot_ktutk
                {

                    pxt:PxNumericalVariable\/12qn\/A01_osuus pxt:hasPrecision 0 ;
                                         pxt:decimals 0 ;
                                         pxt:isPresentationOfDescribedValueDomain ?desdom .
                    ?desdom gsimsf:hasUnit "prosentti" .

                }
            }
            WHERE
            { GRAPH tilasto:tilastot_ktutk
                {

                    pxt:PxNumericalVariable\/12qn\/A01_osuus pxt:hasPrecision ?precision ;
                                         pxt:decimals ?decimals ;
                                         pxt:isPresentationOfDescribedValueDomain ?desdom .
                    ?desdom gsimsf:hasUnit ?unit .

                }
            }
run update, query_formatted:  stat:               <http://www.stat.fi/>

            

            DELETE
            { GRAPH tilasto:tilastot_ktutk
                {
                    gsimsf:Variable\/A01_osuus rdfs:label ?label .

                }
            }
            INSERT
            { GRAPH tilasto:tilastot_ktutk
                {

                    gsimsf:Variable\/A01_osuus  rdfs:label "Elintarvikeet ja alkoholittomat juomat"@fi ;
                               rdfs:label "Livsmedel och alkoholfria drycker"@sv ;
                               rdfs:label "Food and non-alcoholic beverages"@en .

                }
            }
            WHERE
            { GRAPH tilasto:tilastot_ktutk
                {
                    gsimsf:Variable\/A01_osuus rdfs:label ?label

                }
            }
run update, query_formatted:  stat:               <http://www.stat.fi/>

            

            DELETE
            { GRAPH tilasto:tilastot_ktutk
                {
                    gsimsf:Variable\/A01_osuus dc:description ?label .

                }
            }
            INSERT
            { GRAPH tilasto:tilastot_ktutk
                {

                    gsimsf:Variable\/A01_osuus  dc:description ""@fi ;
                                         dc:description ""@sv ;
                                         dc:description ""@en .

                }
            }
            WHERE
            { GRAPH tilasto:tilastot_ktutk
                {
                    gsimsf:Variable\/A01_osuus dc:description ?label

                }
            }
run query, query_formatted:  stat:               <http://www.stat.fi/>

        SELECT  ?coded_var
                ?tech_name
                ?kaikki
                ?heading
                ?unit
                ?jno
                ?rules
                ?presision
                ?decimals
                ?method
                ?filabel
                ?enlabel
                ?svlabel
                ?fidesc
                ?svdesc
                ?endesc

        FROM tilasto:tilastot_ktutk

        WHERE {
            ?pxfile pxt:tableId "12qn" .
            ?pxfile ?kaikki ?dimemsions.
            ?dimemsions pxt:isHeading ?heading .



            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name rdfs:label ?filabel_s .
                BIND (STR(?filabel_s)  AS ?filabel)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?filabel_s),"fi") )
            }
            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name rdfs:label ?enlabel_s .
                BIND (STR(?enlabel_s)  AS ?enlabel)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?enlabel_s),"en") )
            }
            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name rdfs:label ?svlabel_s .
                BIND (STR(?svlabel_s)  AS ?svlabel)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?svlabel_s),"sv") )
            }
            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name dc:description ?fidesc_s .
                BIND (STR(?fidesc_s)  AS ?fidesc)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?fidesc_s),"fi") )
            }
            OPTIONAL {

                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?endesc_s),"en") )

            ?coded_var pxt:hasPrecision ?presision.
            OPTIONAL {
            ?coded_var pxt:decimals ?decimals.

            ?coded_var pxt:isPresentationOfDescribedValueDomain ?d .

                ?tech_name
                ?kaikki

                ?unit
                ?jno

                ?decimals
                ?method
                ?filabel
                ?enlabel
                ?svlabel
                ?fidesc
                ?svdesc
                ?endesc

        FROM tilasto:tilastot_ktutk

        WHERE {
            ?pxfile pxt:tableId "12qn" .
            ?pxfile ?kaikki ?dimemsions.
            ?dimemsions pxt:isHeading ?heading .



            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name rdfs:label ?filabel_s .
                BIND (STR(?filabel_s)  AS ?filabel)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?filabel_s),"fi") )

                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?svlabel_s),"sv") )

                ?tech_name dc:description ?fidesc_s .

                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?fidesc_s),"fi") )

            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name dc:description ?svdesc_s .

                BIND (STR(?endesc_s)  AS ?endesc)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?endesc_s),"en") )

            ?coded_var pxt:hasSequenceNumber ?jno .

            ?coded_var pxt:isPresentationOfDescribedValueDomain ?d .
            ?tech_name gsimsf:hasDescribedValueDomain ?d .
            ?d gsimsf:hasProcessingRules ?rules.
            ?d gsimsf:hasAggregationMethod ?method.
            ?d gsimsf:hasUnit ?unit.

        SELECT  ?coded_var
                ?tech_name
                ?kaikki
                ?heading
                ?unit
                ?jno
                ?rules
                ?presision
                ?decimals
                ?method
                ?filabel
                ?enlabel
                ?svlabel
                ?fidesc
                ?svdesc
                ?endesc

        FROM tilasto:tilastot_ktutk

        WHERE {
            ?pxfile pxt:tableId "12qn" .
            ?pxfile ?kaikki ?dimemsions.
            ?dimemsions pxt:isHeading ?heading .



            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name rdfs:label ?filabel_s .
                BIND (STR(?filabel_s)  AS ?filabel)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?filabel_s),"fi") )
            }
            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name rdfs:label ?enlabel_s .
                BIND (STR(?enlabel_s)  AS ?enlabel)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?enlabel_s),"en") )
            }
            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name rdfs:label ?svlabel_s .
                BIND (STR(?svlabel_s)  AS ?svlabel)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?svlabel_s),"sv") )
            }
            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name dc:description ?fidesc_s .
                BIND (STR(?fidesc_s)  AS ?fidesc)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?fidesc_s),"fi") )
            }
            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name dc:description ?svdesc_s .
                BIND (STR(?svdesc_s)  AS ?svdesc)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?svdesc_s),"sv") )
            }
            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name dc:description ?endesc_s .
                BIND (STR(?endesc_s)  AS ?endesc)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?endesc_s),"en") )
            }

            ?dimemsions pxt:hasNumericalVariable ?coded_var .

            ?coded_var pxt:hasSequenceNumber ?jno .
            ?coded_var pxt:hasPrecision ?presision.
            OPTIONAL {
            ?coded_var pxt:decimals ?decimals.
            }
            ?coded_var pxt:isPresentationOfDescribedValueDomain ?d .
            ?tech_name gsimsf:hasDescribedValueDomain ?d .
            ?d gsimsf:hasProcessingRules ?rules.
            ?d gsimsf:hasAggregationMethod ?method.
            ?d gsimsf:hasUnit ?unit.


        }
run update, query_formatted:  stat:               <http://www.stat.fi/>

        SELECT  ?coded_var
                ?tech_name
                ?kaikki
                ?heading
                ?unit
                ?jno
                ?rules
                ?presision
                ?decimals
                ?method
                ?filabel
                ?enlabel
                ?svlabel
                ?fidesc
                ?svdesc
                ?endesc

        FROM tilasto:tilastot_ktutk

        WHERE {
            ?pxfile pxt:tableId "12qn" .
            ?pxfile ?kaikki ?dimemsions.
            ?dimemsions pxt:isHeading ?heading .



            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name rdfs:label ?filabel_s .
                BIND (STR(?filabel_s)  AS ?filabel)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?filabel_s),"fi") )
            }
            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name rdfs:label ?enlabel_s .
                BIND (STR(?enlabel_s)  AS ?enlabel)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?enlabel_s),"en") )
            }
            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name rdfs:label ?svlabel_s .
                BIND (STR(?svlabel_s)  AS ?svlabel)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?svlabel_s),"sv") )
            }
            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name dc:description ?fidesc_s .
                BIND (STR(?fidesc_s)  AS ?fidesc)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?fidesc_s),"fi") )
            }
            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name dc:description ?svdesc_s .
                BIND (STR(?svdesc_s)  AS ?svdesc)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?svdesc_s),"sv") )
            }
            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name dc:description ?endesc_s .
                BIND (STR(?endesc_s)  AS ?endesc)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?endesc_s),"en") )
            }

            ?dimemsions pxt:hasNumericalVariable ?coded_var .

            ?coded_var pxt:hasSequenceNumber ?jno .
            ?coded_var pxt:hasPrecision ?presision.
            OPTIONAL {
            ?coded_var pxt:decimals ?decimals.
            }
            ?coded_var pxt:isPresentationOfDescribedValueDomain ?d .
            ?tech_name gsimsf:hasDescribedValueDomain ?d .
            ?d gsimsf:hasProcessingRules ?rules.
            ?d gsimsf:hasAggregationMethod ?method.
            ?d gsimsf:hasUnit ?unit.


        }
run update, query_formatted:  stat:               <http://www.stat.fi/>

            
			DELETE 
                { GRAPH tilasto:tilastot_ktutk
                    {

                    pxt:PxNumericalVariable\/12qn\/A12_osuus a pxt_ont:PxNumericalVariable ;
                                        pxt:hasSequenceNumber ?NRO ;
                                        pxt:hasPrecision ?PRES ;
                                        pxt:decimals ?DESIM ;
                                        pxt:isPresentationOfDescribedValueDomain gsimsf:DescribedValueDomain\/A12_osuus .
                    }
                }			
            INSERT 
                { GRAPH tilasto:tilastot_ktutk
                    {

                    pxt:PxNumericalVariable\/12qn\/A12_osuus a pxt_ont:PxNumericalVariable ;

                                        pxt:hasPrecision 0 ;
                                        pxt:decimals 0 ;
                                        pxt:isPresentationOfDescribedValueDomain gsimsf:DescribedValueDomain\/A12_osuus .

DELETE
{ GRAPH tilasto:tilastot_ktutk
	{
		?cube cubemeta:source ?text .
	   
	}
}
INSERT
{ GRAPH tilasto:tilastot_ktutk
	{
	   
		?cube   cubemeta:source " kotitalouksien kulutus"@fi ;
				cubemeta:source " hush√•llens konsumtion"@sv ;
				cubemeta:source "households' consumption"@en .
	}
}
WHERE
{ GRAPH tilasto:tilastot_ktutk
	{
		?pxfile pxt:tableId "12qn" .
		?pxfile pxt:isPresentationOf ?cube .

		?cube cubemeta:source ?text .
		
	}
}
run query, query_formatted:  stat:               <http://www.stat.fi/>

            

                SELECT ?updated_date ?user
                FROM tilasto:tilastot_ktutk
                WHERE {
                    ?pxfile pxt:tableId "12qn".
                    ?pxfile pxt:isPresentationOf ?cube.
                    ?cube cubemeta:lastUpdated ?updated_date.
                  ?cube cubemeta:modifier ?user.
                }
run update, query_formatted:  stat:               <http://www.stat.fi/>

            

                DELETE
                { GRAPH tilasto:tilastot_ktutk
                    {
                        ?pxfile pxt:tableId "12qn" .
                        ?pxfile pxt:isPresentationOf ?cube .
                        ?cube cubemeta:lastUpdated ?updated_date .
                        ?cube cubemeta:modifier ?user .
                    }
                }
                INSERT
                { GRAPH tilasto:tilastot_ktutk
                    {
                        ?pxfile pxt:tableId "12qn".
                        ?pxfile pxt:isPresentationOf ?cube.
                        ?cube cubemeta:lastUpdated ?timeVal .
                        ?cube cubemeta:modifier "Miettinj" .
                    }
                }
                WHERE
                { GRAPH tilasto:tilastot_ktutk
                    {
                        ?pxfile pxt:tableId "12qn".
                        ?pxfile pxt:isPresentationOf ?cube.
                        ?cube cubemeta:lastUpdated ?updated_date.
                        ?cube cubemeta:modifier ?user.
    					BIND(now() AS ?timeVal) .
                    }
				}
run query, query_formatted:  stat:               <http://www.stat.fi/>

                ?tech_name
                ?kaikki
                ?heading
                ?unit
                ?jno
                ?rules
                ?presision
                ?decimals
                ?method
                ?filabel
                ?enlabel
                ?svlabel
                ?fidesc
                ?svdesc
                ?endesc

        FROM tilasto:tilastot_ktutk

        WHERE {
            ?pxfile pxt:tableId "14q7" .
            ?pxfile ?kaikki ?dimemsions.
            ?dimemsions pxt:isHeading ?heading .



            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name rdfs:label ?filabel_s .
                BIND (STR(?filabel_s)  AS ?filabel)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?filabel_s),"fi") )
            }
            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name rdfs:label ?enlabel_s .
                BIND (STR(?enlabel_s)  AS ?enlabel)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?enlabel_s),"en") )
            }
            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name rdfs:label ?svlabel_s .
                BIND (STR(?svlabel_s)  AS ?svlabel)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?svlabel_s),"sv") )
            }
            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name dc:description ?fidesc_s .
                BIND (STR(?fidesc_s)  AS ?fidesc)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?fidesc_s),"fi") )
            }
            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name dc:description ?svdesc_s .
                BIND (STR(?svdesc_s)  AS ?svdesc)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?svdesc_s),"sv") )
            }
            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name dc:description ?endesc_s .
                BIND (STR(?endesc_s)  AS ?endesc)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?endesc_s),"en") )
            }

            ?dimemsions pxt:hasNumericalVariable ?coded_var .

            ?coded_var pxt:hasSequenceNumber ?jno .
            ?coded_var pxt:hasPrecision ?presision.
            OPTIONAL {
            ?coded_var pxt:decimals ?decimals.
            }
            ?coded_var pxt:isPresentationOfDescribedValueDomain ?d .
            ?tech_name gsimsf:hasDescribedValueDomain ?d .
            ?d gsimsf:hasProcessingRules ?rules.
            ?d gsimsf:hasAggregationMethod ?method.
            ?d gsimsf:hasUnit ?unit.


        }
run update, query_formatted:  stat:               <http://www.stat.fi/>

        SELECT  ?coded_var
                ?tech_name
                ?kaikki
                ?heading
                ?unit
                ?jno
                ?rules
                ?presision
                ?decimals
                ?method
                ?filabel
                ?enlabel
                ?svlabel
                ?fidesc
                ?svdesc
                ?endesc

        FROM tilasto:tilastot_ktutk

        WHERE {
            ?pxfile pxt:tableId "14q7" .
            ?pxfile ?kaikki ?dimemsions.
            ?dimemsions pxt:isHeading ?heading .



            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name rdfs:label ?filabel_s .
                BIND (STR(?filabel_s)  AS ?filabel)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?filabel_s),"fi") )
            }
            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name rdfs:label ?enlabel_s .
                BIND (STR(?enlabel_s)  AS ?enlabel)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?enlabel_s),"en") )
            }
            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name rdfs:label ?svlabel_s .
                BIND (STR(?svlabel_s)  AS ?svlabel)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?svlabel_s),"sv") )
            }
            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name dc:description ?fidesc_s .
                BIND (STR(?fidesc_s)  AS ?fidesc)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?fidesc_s),"fi") )
            }
            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name dc:description ?svdesc_s .
                BIND (STR(?svdesc_s)  AS ?svdesc)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?svdesc_s),"sv") )
            }
            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name dc:description ?endesc_s .
                BIND (STR(?endesc_s)  AS ?endesc)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?endesc_s),"en") )
            }

            ?dimemsions pxt:hasNumericalVariable ?coded_var .

            ?coded_var pxt:hasSequenceNumber ?jno .
            ?coded_var pxt:hasPrecision ?presision.
            OPTIONAL {
            ?coded_var pxt:decimals ?decimals.
            }
            ?coded_var pxt:isPresentationOfDescribedValueDomain ?d .
            ?tech_name gsimsf:hasDescribedValueDomain ?d .
            ?d gsimsf:hasProcessingRules ?rules.
            ?d gsimsf:hasAggregationMethod ?method.
            ?d gsimsf:hasUnit ?unit.


        }
run update, query_formatted:  stat:               <http://www.stat.fi/>

                                         pxt:decimals ?decimals ;
                                         pxt:isPresentationOfDescribedValueDomain ?desdom .
                    ?desdom gsimsf:hasUnit ?unit .

                }
            }
run update, query_formatted:  stat:               <http://www.stat.fi/>

                SELECT ?updated_date ?user
                FROM tilasto:tilastot_ktutk
                WHERE {
                    ?pxfile pxt:tableId "14q7".
                    ?pxfile pxt:isPresentationOf ?cube.
                    ?cube cubemeta:lastUpdated ?updated_date.
                  ?cube cubemeta:modifier ?user.
                }
run update, query_formatted:  stat:               <http://www.stat.fi/>

            

                DELETE
                { GRAPH tilasto:tilastot_ktutk
                    {
                        ?pxfile pxt:tableId "14q7" .
                        ?pxfile pxt:isPresentationOf ?cube .
                        ?cube cubemeta:lastUpdated ?updated_date .
                        ?cube cubemeta:modifier ?user .
                    }
                }
                INSERT
                { GRAPH tilasto:tilastot_ktutk
                    {
                        ?pxfile pxt:tableId "14q7".
                        ?pxfile pxt:isPresentationOf ?cube.
                        ?cube cubemeta:lastUpdated ?timeVal .
                        ?cube cubemeta:modifier "Miettinj" .
                    }
                }
                WHERE
                { GRAPH tilasto:tilastot_ktutk
                    {
                        ?pxfile pxt:tableId "14q7".
                        ?pxfile pxt:isPresentationOf ?cube.
                        ?cube cubemeta:lastUpdated ?updated_date.
                        ?cube cubemeta:modifier ?user.
    					BIND(now() AS ?timeVal) .
                    }
				}
run query, query_formatted:  stat:               <http://www.stat.fi/>

            
         
SELECT   
?filabel
?enlabel 
?svlabel
?fidesc
?svdesc
?endesc
?finote
?ennote
?svnote
?fisource
?ensource
?svsource
?ficontact
?encontact
?svcontact

                FROM tilasto:tilastot_ktutk

                WHERE {


                    OPTIONAL {
                        cubemeta:CubeMeta\/14q7 dc:title ?filabel_s .
                        BIND (STR(?filabel_s)  AS ?filabel)
                        FILTER( langMatches(lang(?filabel_s),"fi") )
                    }
                    OPTIONAL {
                        cubemeta:CubeMeta\/14q7 dc:title ?svlabel_s .
                        BIND (STR(?svlabel_s)  AS ?svlabel)
                        FILTER( langMatches(lang(?svlabel_s),"sv") )
                    }
                    OPTIONAL {
                        cubemeta:CubeMeta\/14q7 dc:title ?enlabel_s .
                        BIND (STR(?enlabel_s)  AS ?enlabel)
                        FILTER( langMatches(lang(?enlabel_s),"en") )
                    }
                    OPTIONAL {
                        cubemeta:CubeMeta\/14q7 dc:description ?fidesc_s .
                        BIND (STR(?fidesc_s)  AS ?fidesc)
                        FILTER( langMatches(lang(?fidesc_s),"fi") )
                    }
                    OPTIONAL {
                        cubemeta:CubeMeta\/14q7 dc:description ?svdesc_s .
                        BIND (STR(?svdesc_s)  AS ?svdesc)
                        FILTER( langMatches(lang(?svdesc_s),"sv") )
                    }
                    OPTIONAL {
                        cubemeta:CubeMeta\/14q7 dc:description ?endesc_s .
                        BIND (STR(?endesc_s)  AS ?endesc)
                        FILTER( langMatches(lang(?endesc_s),"en") )
                    }
                    OPTIONAL {
                        cubemeta:CubeMeta\/14q7 cubemeta:tableNote ?finote_s .
                        BIND (STR(?finote_s)  AS ?finote)
                        FILTER( langMatches(lang(?finote_s),"fi") )
                    }
                    OPTIONAL {
                        cubemeta:CubeMeta\/14q7 cubemeta:tableNote ?svnote_s .
                        BIND (STR(?svnote_s)  AS ?svnote)
                        FILTER( langMatches(lang(?svnote_s),"sv") )
                    }
                    OPTIONAL {
                        cubemeta:CubeMeta\/14q7 cubemeta:tableNote ?ennote_s .
                        BIND (STR(?ennote_s)  AS ?ennote)
                        FILTER( langMatches(lang(?ennote_s),"en") )
                    }
                    OPTIONAL {
                        cubemeta:CubeMeta\/14q7 cubemeta:source ?fisource_s .
                        BIND (STR(?fisource_s)  AS ?fisource)
                        FILTER( langMatches(lang(?fisource_s),"fi") )
                    }
                    OPTIONAL {
                        cubemeta:CubeMeta\/14q7 cubemeta:source ?svsource_s .
                        BIND (STR(?svsource_s)  AS ?svsource)
                        FILTER( langMatches(lang(?svsource_s),"sv") )
                    }
                    OPTIONAL {
                        cubemeta:CubeMeta\/14q7 cubemeta:source ?ensource_s .
                        BIND (STR(?ensource_s)  AS ?ensource)
                        FILTER( langMatches(lang(?ensource_s),"en") )
                    }
                    OPTIONAL {
                        cubemeta:CubeMeta\/14q7 cubemeta:contact ?ficontact_s .
                        BIND (STR(?ficontact_s)  AS ?ficontact)
                        FILTER( langMatches(lang(?ficontact_s),"fi") )
                    }
                    OPTIONAL {
                        cubemeta:CubeMeta\/14q7 cubemeta:contact ?svcontact_s .
                        BIND (STR(?svcontact_s)  AS ?svcontact)
                        FILTER( langMatches(lang(?svcontact_s),"sv") )
                    }
                    OPTIONAL {
                        cubemeta:CubeMeta\/14q7 cubemeta:contact ?encontact_s .
                        BIND (STR(?encontact_s)  AS ?encontact)
                        FILTER( langMatches(lang(?encontact_s),"en") )
                    }

                }
run query, query_formatted:  stat:               <http://www.stat.fi/>

        SELECT  ?coded_var
                ?tech_name
                ?kaikki
                ?heading
                ?unit
                ?jno
                ?rules
                ?presision
                ?decimals
                ?method
                ?filabel
                ?enlabel
                ?svlabel
                ?fidesc
                ?svdesc
                ?endesc

        FROM tilasto:tilastot_ktutk

        WHERE {
            ?pxfile pxt:tableId "14q7" .
            ?pxfile ?kaikki ?dimemsions.
            ?dimemsions pxt:isHeading ?heading .



            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name rdfs:label ?filabel_s .
                BIND (STR(?filabel_s)  AS ?filabel)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?filabel_s),"fi") )
            }
            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name rdfs:label ?enlabel_s .
                BIND (STR(?enlabel_s)  AS ?enlabel)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?enlabel_s),"en") )
            }
            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name rdfs:label ?svlabel_s .
                BIND (STR(?svlabel_s)  AS ?svlabel)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?svlabel_s),"sv") )
            }
            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name dc:description ?fidesc_s .
                BIND (STR(?fidesc_s)  AS ?fidesc)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?fidesc_s),"fi") )
            }
            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name dc:description ?svdesc_s .
                BIND (STR(?svdesc_s)  AS ?svdesc)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?svdesc_s),"sv") )
            }
            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name dc:description ?endesc_s .
                BIND (STR(?endesc_s)  AS ?endesc)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?endesc_s),"en") )
            }

            ?dimemsions pxt:hasNumericalVariable ?coded_var .

            ?coded_var pxt:hasSequenceNumber ?jno .
            ?coded_var pxt:hasPrecision ?presision.
            OPTIONAL {
            ?coded_var pxt:decimals ?decimals.
            }
            ?coded_var pxt:isPresentationOfDescribedValueDomain ?d .
            ?tech_name gsimsf:hasDescribedValueDomain ?d .
            ?d gsimsf:hasProcessingRules ?rules.
            ?d gsimsf:hasAggregationMethod ?method.
            ?d gsimsf:hasUnit ?unit.


        }
run query, query_formatted:  stat:               <http://www.stat.fi/>

        SELECT  ?coded_var
                ?tech_name
                ?kaikki
                ?heading
                ?unit
                ?jno
                ?rules
                ?presision
                ?decimals
                ?method
                ?filabel
                ?enlabel
                ?svlabel
                ?fidesc
                ?svdesc
                ?endesc

        FROM tilasto:tilastot_ktutk

        WHERE {
            ?pxfile pxt:tableId "14q8" .
            ?pxfile ?kaikki ?dimemsions.
            ?dimemsions pxt:isHeading ?heading .



            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name rdfs:label ?filabel_s .
                BIND (STR(?filabel_s)  AS ?filabel)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?filabel_s),"fi") )
            }
            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name rdfs:label ?enlabel_s .
                BIND (STR(?enlabel_s)  AS ?enlabel)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?enlabel_s),"en") )
            }
            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name rdfs:label ?svlabel_s .
                BIND (STR(?svlabel_s)  AS ?svlabel)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?svlabel_s),"sv") )
            }
            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name dc:description ?fidesc_s .
                BIND (STR(?fidesc_s)  AS ?fidesc)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?fidesc_s),"fi") )
            }
            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name dc:description ?svdesc_s .
                BIND (STR(?svdesc_s)  AS ?svdesc)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?svdesc_s),"sv") )
            }
            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name dc:description ?endesc_s .
                BIND (STR(?endesc_s)  AS ?endesc)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?endesc_s),"en") )
            }

            ?dimemsions pxt:hasNumericalVariable ?coded_var .

            ?coded_var pxt:hasSequenceNumber ?jno .
            ?coded_var pxt:hasPrecision ?presision.
            OPTIONAL {
            ?coded_var pxt:decimals ?decimals.
            }
            ?coded_var pxt:isPresentationOfDescribedValueDomain ?d .
            ?tech_name gsimsf:hasDescribedValueDomain ?d .
            ?d gsimsf:hasProcessingRules ?rules.
            ?d gsimsf:hasAggregationMethod ?method.
            ?d gsimsf:hasUnit ?unit.


        }
run update, query_formatted:  stat:               <http://www.stat.fi/>

        SELECT  ?coded_var
                ?tech_name
                ?kaikki
                ?heading
                ?unit
                ?jno
                ?rules
                ?presision
                ?decimals
                ?method
                ?filabel
                ?enlabel
                ?svlabel
                ?fidesc
                ?svdesc
                ?endesc

        FROM tilasto:tilastot_ktutk

        WHERE {
            ?pxfile pxt:tableId "14q8" .
            ?pxfile ?kaikki ?dimemsions.
            ?dimemsions pxt:isHeading ?heading .



            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name rdfs:label ?filabel_s .
                BIND (STR(?filabel_s)  AS ?filabel)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?filabel_s),"fi") )
            }
            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name rdfs:label ?enlabel_s .
                BIND (STR(?enlabel_s)  AS ?enlabel)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?enlabel_s),"en") )
            }
            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name rdfs:label ?svlabel_s .
                BIND (STR(?svlabel_s)  AS ?svlabel)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?svlabel_s),"sv") )
            }
            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name dc:description ?fidesc_s .
                BIND (STR(?fidesc_s)  AS ?fidesc)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?fidesc_s),"fi") )
            }
            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name dc:description ?svdesc_s .
                BIND (STR(?svdesc_s)  AS ?svdesc)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?svdesc_s),"sv") )
            }
            OPTIONAL {
                ?tech_name dc:description ?endesc_s .
                BIND (STR(?endesc_s)  AS ?endesc)
                FILTER( langMatches(lang(?endesc_s),"en") )
            }

            ?dimemsions pxt:hasNumericalVariable ?coded_var .

            ?coded_var pxt:hasSequenceNumber ?jno .
            ?coded_var pxt:hasPrecision ?presision.
            OPTIONAL {
            ?coded_var pxt:decimals ?decimals.
            }
            ?coded_var pxt:isPresentationOfDescribedValueDomain ?d .
            ?tech_name gsimsf:hasDescribedValueDomain ?d .
            ?d gsimsf:hasProcessingRules ?rules.
            ?d gsimsf:hasAggregationMethod ?method.
            ?d gsimsf:hasUnit ?unit.


        }
run update, query_formatted:  stat:               <http://www.stat.fi/>

                                        pxt:decimals ?DESIM ;
